descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see...a 17x17 grid that is split into 9 5x5 squares. Inside of these 9 blocks you should see blocks of the same color.
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to...replicate what is inside of the top left 5x5 grid throughout the rest of the 8 grid left. The color of these additional blocks should match the color of the block cut line.
